text:
Tenka-chan...! It's getting late,
you'll be late if you don't get up soon~!

...N-No way... It's...
cold... outside the blanket...

...! Tenka-chan! Amana's room has the heater on,
so it's really warm!

Amana will bring Tenka-chan's clothes, right?
So, if Tenka-chan moves while staying in bed──

Geez, you're praising me too much~
...Well then, let's go to Amana's room~!
